    Command handler for closing the currently open database catalog.

    Command handler for counting rows in a table that match a specific criterion.

    Command handler for creating a new table in the database.

    Command handler for exiting the application.

    Command handler for importing a table from a text file into the database.

    Command handler for performing an inner join operation on two tables.
    InsertCommand

    OpenCommand
    Command handler for opening a database catalog file.
    PrintCommand
    Command handler for displaying the contents of a table with pagination.
    RenameCommand
    Command handler for renaming an existing table in the database.
    SaveAsCommand
    Command handler for saving the current database (catalog and all modified tables) to a new specified catalog file path.
    SaveCommand
    Command handler for saving the current state of the database (catalog and modified tables) to its existing file paths.
    SelectCommand
    Command handler for selecting and displaying rows from a table that match a specific criterion.
    ShowTablesCommand
    Command handler for displaying a list of all tables registered in the current database catalog.
    UpdateCommand
    Command handler for updating values in rows of a table that match a specific criterion.
